data.description: Welcome to your Modern Dream Home! FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN at 2.6%. This stylish residence that is in the Oak Park neighborhood boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a sense of spaciousness and flow. The kitchen is adorned with stunning granite countertops and backsplash which not only provide ample workspace but also add an elegant touch to the modern design. The spacious backyard is perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. It is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch and any investor out there can easily ad an ADU with it's own entrance towards the alleyway. Come check out this beauty!
